---
import { getEmDashCollection } from "emdash";

const { entries: posts } = await getEmDashCollection("posts");
const hasPosts = posts.length > 0;
---

{hasPosts && (
<section id="blog" data-section="blog" class="py-16 md:py-24 px-6 lg:px-12">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-start md:items-end mb-10 md:mb-12 gap-4 md:gap-6">
      <div class="max-w-2xl">
        <h3 class="font-display text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-main mb-3 md:mb-4 tracking-tight">El Diario.</h3>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-muted font-light leading-relaxed">Reflexiones sobre psicología, psicoanálisis y el arte de vivir de forma más consciente.</p>
      </div>
      <a href="/blog" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 font-bold text-main hover:text-accent transition-colors uppercase tracking-wider text-xs md:text-sm border-b border-main hover:border-accent pb-1 mt-4 md:mt-0">
        Ver todo el blog <i data-lucide="arrow-right" class="w-3 h-3 md:w-4 md:h-4"></i>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div data-stagger class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 md:gap-8" data-section="blog-grid">
      <article class="group cursor-pointer">
        <div class="aspect-[16/9] md:aspect-[4/3] rounded-[1.5rem] md:rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden mb-4 md:mb-6 border border-main/10 shadow-soft">
          <img src="/images/blog-beach.jpeg" alt="Blog post" class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700 ease-in-out opacity-90">
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3 items-center text-[10px] md:text-xs font-bold text-accent uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 md:mb-3">
          <span>Ansiedad</span>
          <span class="text-main/30">•</span>
          <span>5 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-display text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-main mb-2 md:mb-3 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors leading-tight">El impacto oculto de la autoexigencia constante</h4>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-muted font-light line-clamp-2 leading-relaxed">Vivimos en una sociedad que premia el perfeccionismo, pero a puerta cerrada, el coste emocional es altísimo y a menudo silencioso.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="group cursor-pointer">
        <div class="aspect-[16/9] md:aspect-[4/3] rounded-[1.5rem] md:rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden mb-4 md:mb-6 border border-main/10 shadow-soft">
          <img src="/images/blog-sunset.jpeg" alt="Blog post" class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700 ease-in-out opacity-90">
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3 items-center text-[10px] md:text-xs font-bold text-accent uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 md:mb-3">
          <span>Psicoanálisis</span>
          <span class="text-main/30">•</span>
          <span>8 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-display text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-main mb-2 md:mb-3 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors leading-tight">¿En qué se diferencia el psicoanálisis de otras terapias?</h4>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-muted font-light line-clamp-2 leading-relaxed">Una guía práctica para entender por qué rascar la superficie a veces no es suficiente para sanar las heridas más profundas.</p>
      </article>

      <article class="group cursor-pointer sm:col-span-2 md:col-span-1">
        <div class="aspect-[16/9] md:aspect-[4/3] rounded-[1.5rem] md:rounded-[2rem] overflow-hidden mb-4 md:mb-6 border border-main/10 shadow-soft">
          <img src="/images/blog-lake.jpeg" alt="Blog post" class="w-full h-full object-cover transform group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700 ease-in-out opacity-90">
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-3 items-center text-[10px] md:text-xs font-bold text-accent uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 md:mb-3">
          <span>Relaciones</span>
          <span class="text-main/30">•</span>
          <span>6 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h4 class="font-display text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-main mb-2 md:mb-3 group-hover:text-accent transition-colors leading-tight">Los límites: El acto de amor propio más difícil</h4>
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base text-muted font-light line-clamp-2 leading-relaxed">Aprender a decir 'no' sin culpa es fundamental para construir relaciones sanas, duraderas y basadas en el respeto mutuo.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
)}
